What to do with older holostates?
Version	Action	Rationale
SOREIN#00 & #01	Archive to /SMRIF/02_holostates/archive/ (or zip). Keep full text; tag as superseded.	They capture origin myth + first recursion but contain heavier symbol clutter now pruned.
