Any experimental/branch holostates	Merge or discard if content already ported into Orchard leaves/Fork notes.	Prevent redundancy; reference via Orchard where needed.

    Rule of Thumb:

        Latest full holostate (this file) stays in /02_holostates/ root.

        One delta-trim predecessor stays nearby.

        Everything earlier lives in /archive/ or gets compressed into “delta diff” notes.

Feel free to adjust naming or directory conventions.
